{"tid":702444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【難為清潔工】強國萬人龍蝦宴 一晚製造30噸垃圾","createTime":"2018-06-15T02:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T02:05:19.000Z","uid":39464,"like":120,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"12ed8387d1c2c7a51c35ccf6a5ab9c33e40cde5e","tid":702444,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T02:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180614/large/1528988194_b898.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180614%2Flarge%2F1528988194_b898.jpg&h=e721d29f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n太恐怖了，真難為一班清潔工！踏入6月，恰是小龍蝦飄香時。江蘇盱眙（金誠）舉行一年一度的國際龍蝦節「萬人龍蝦宴」，今年吸引5萬海內外食客慕名而來，各種口味的龍蝦輪番上陣，一夜掃光50噸小龍蝦。但活動結束後，現場盡是蝦殼、啤酒瓶等垃圾，慘不忍堵，當局出動了300名清潔工清出30多噸垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n萬人宴於13日下午4時在都梁廣場如約開席，當地百家商戶提供的50噸龍蝦，雖然室外氣溫高達36&deg;C，熱浪逼人，但無阻「蝦粉」從四面八方趕到。南京人、上海人、安徽人，美國人、英國人......大家成群結隊而來。到了晚上6時，不少晚到的食客已經找不到位置，只能在看台上佔位置。作為內地最大的露天山地廣場，都梁廣場整整擺了1,200桌，再加上全城多個餐飲賓館的分會場同時啟動，共計5萬名食客在小城盱眙的四面八方上演了同吃小龍蝦的壯觀場景。<br />\n<br />\n食客吃的津津有味，但難為了一班負責善後的清潔工人。活動結束後，由於蝦殼、啤酒瓶等散滿着整個廣場，當局出動300名清潔工，耗時5個多小時共清理各類垃圾30餘噸，搬離桌椅2萬多張，至於14日淩晨才清理完畢，才有世間吃宵夜。<br />\n<br />\n「搞這樣無聊的吉尼斯（健力士）紀錄有意義嗎？彰顯了甚麼？醜陋的暴露、道德的淪喪！主辦者為何不敢申報『現場不留一點垃圾』的萬人龍蝦宴呢？！」「辦理這樣的活動有甚麼意義嗎？再說了主辦方賺了錢，搞衞生的事非得環衞工人去嗎？」「這大概就是中國群眾活動的一個縮影吧，主辦方應該向國外辦活動一樣，各人垃圾各人清理，要有環境意識！」內地網民對當局大搞龍蝦宴，遺留大量垃圾大感不滿，人為應該自己吃，還得自己掃！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180615/large/1528992994_8af7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180615%2Flarge%2F1528992994_8af7.jpg&h=cc063856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180615/large/1528992995_f09a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180615%2Flarge%2F1528992995_f09a.jpg&h=532c8e61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180615/large/1528992996_a797.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180615%2Flarge%2F1528992996_a797.jpg&h=b6481614&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180615/large/1528992997_3ec4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180615%2Flarge%2F1528992997_3ec4.jpg&h=9f1e310a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180615/large/1528992999_98b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180615%2Flarge%2F1528992999_98b5.jpg&h=106c7c1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180615/58316882\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58316882&d=bNbl%2FLWCCKDu5uVJf5jIbZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=f90c87b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58316882&h=0b06d079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180615/58316882</a>"},{"pid":"4aa624f3ae18283db10a603b6a507e71b3ffa96f","tid":702444,"uid":13303,"like":308,"dislike":3,"score":305,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T02:04:47.000Z","msg":"垃圾食垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76adda2a460b1e5515c3ce53061858fa3a21f654","tid":702444,"uid":2772,"like":294,"dislike":1,"score":293,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T02:07:17.000Z","msg":"「萬人龍蝦宴」，今年吸引5萬海內外食客慕名而來，各種口味的龍蝦輪番上陣，一夜掃光50噸<span style=\"color: red;\">小龍蝦</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005725481c05d88fd0238e32a928bf7065e830ec","tid":702444,"uid":2772,"like":264,"dislike":3,"score":261,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"